OL,4,CWater companies illegally dumping
OL,5,Csewage in England and Wales' rivers
OL,6, Water companies have been illegally
OL,7, dumping untreated sewage into rivers in
OL,8, England and Wales, an investigation by
OL,9, BBC Panorama has found.
OL,11,FData analysed by the programme showed
OL,12,Fsome companies have regularly breached
OL,13,Fthe conditions in their permits.
OL,15,FTreatment works are only allowed to put
OL,16,Fsewage into waterways after wet weather
OL,17,Fand when they are close to capacity.
OL,19,FThe water industry says it will invest
OL,20,Fmore than a billion pounds over five
OL,21,Fyears to reduce discharges into rivers.
